'''Childhood cataract''' is [[cataract]] that occurs at birth or in childhood.<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Medsinge|first=Anagha|last2=Nischal|first2=Ken K.|date=2015-01-01|title=Pediatric cataract: challenges and future directions|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC4293928/pdf/opth-9-077.pdf|journal=Clinical Ophthalmology|location=Auckland, N.Z.|volume=9|pages=77–90|doi=10.2147/OPTH.S59009|issn=1177-5467|pmc=4293928|pmid=25609909}}</ref> It may be [[Congenital cataract|congenital]] or acquired.
